thread.title: Chris Hall
thread.title_full: Frames Direct reviewed by Chris Hall

author: Chris Hall
title: Chris Hall
text:
I expect near immediate confirmation of prescriptions. Adding the option of express shipping should include a disclaimer about the order processing time. I needed quick turn around and this didn't fit the bill. I ordered from my regular place 3 days after ordering from you and it arrived first.
Wont use FramesDirect Again.
